column1: MWRA Harbor Water Clarity Measurements, collected 1994 through 2019
Attenuation coefficient and TSS is measured only at nutrient monitoring stations (137, 138, 024, 038, 140, 139, 124, 141, 142, 130).
Secchi depth and light attenuation were measured beginning in 1994; TSS measured prior to 1996 was suspect due to method problems.
Marine stations only are shown, no freshwater.  Blank data cells indicate that data was either suspect or not collected.
